100 Traps.description: Navigate an obstacle course filled with 100 challenging level.

1v1.description: Face off in quick, round-based duels designed to test individual skill and aim.

Arms Race.description: Progress through a weapon ladder by securing kills in a free-for-all battle.

Bhop.description: Bunny hop through maps requiring speed, timing, and movement mastery.

Combat Surf.description: Surf maps with weapons, blending movement skills and combat.

Course.description: Complete jump and movement-based challenges to reach the end.

Deathrun.description: Runners dodge traps while one player (the “Death”) activates them.

Executes.description: Practice or simulate bombsite takes with utility and team coordination.

Gun Game.description: Climb through a tiered weapon list with each kill, ending with a knife.

Hide and Seek.description: One team hides while the other hunts them down with limited time.

KZ.description: Climb timed jump maps using precision movement and optimal strafing.

Minigames.description: A rotation of quick, fun, and often chaotic bite-sized challenges.

Mirror Madness.description: Competitive style game mode but with mirrored maps.

One In the Chamber.description: One bullet per life — miss and you're vulnerable until a kill.

Only Up.description: Ascend a punishing vertical course — one mistake, and it’s back to start.

Retakes.description: Practice retaking bombsites in fast-paced, scenario-driven rounds.

ScoutzKnives.description: High-flying low-gravity battles with scouts and knives only.

Scrims.description: Structured 5v5 matches for practice, coordination, and competition.

Surf.description: Glide along angled ramps using movement mechanics to reach the end.

Tag.description: Classic playground-style tag in custom CS2 maps — don’t get caught.
